description: Studying? No❌. Practicing H-O-T-T-O-G-O? Duhhh ✅. Who’s excited for BLUES PONY PUB this Friday 🦄💅🎀??? Can’t wait to see you all there, 4-9PM in the EUS common room!!! 🎉

I know🧠 you wanted me to stay📍But I can’t ignore the crazy visions👁️ of me in Blues Pub🍺 And I heard👂 that there’s a special place🌃 Where boys and girls👫 can all be queens👑 every single day. I’m having wicked dreams💭 of leaving the library📚 And McConnell Engineering Building, I swear it’s calling me📞Won’t make my mama🤱 proud, it’s gonna cause a scene. She sees her baby girl👶, I know she’s gonna scream🗣️…

Your favourite design team’s favourite design teams present…

BLUES💙PONY🐴PUB💅💖🎀✨

Join us Friday November 22nd, 4-9PM in the EUS Common Room because “You know what they say: Never waste a Friday night on a first date”🔥🔥🔥. Dress code is HOTTOGO. Drag is strongly encouraged💃💃💃 so don’t be afraid to whip out your Mini skirt and go-go boots👢The best Chapell will win a super epic prize🎁 good luck babe!

In an effort to be more sustainable, please remember your own reusable cup! This is an 18+ event and is CASH ONLY. 
*Accessibility Informatoon*
- There will be vegetarian food options, as well as non-alcoholic and gluten free drinks available for purchase 🥤
- Blues pub is typically a loud and crowded event 🕺
- McConnell Engineering Building has elevator access to each floor, wheelchair accessible entrances, gender neutral, and accessible bathrooms, and is a smoke free environment.
